In fulfillment of the requirement from section 2.4.6 of the Academic
Regulations in Princeton's Rights, Rules, Responsibilities guide,
and the COS 217 Generative AI policy, disclose and describe how you
used AI in completing this assignment:

We used AI to help me check for some of the invariants we missed
in part 2 of the assignment after we could not brainstorm any more
(used it for node cannot be its own parent). We also used it to
brainstorm our design idea for part 3 - we initially had 2 types of
nodes with nodeDir and nodeFile, and then after we realized that
implementation was a little tricky for the ft.c, we consulted AI
on how to consolidate into a new version. 

